OL,3,C'Second mum' to hostage twins on the
OL,4,Cdesperate wait for their release
OL,6,FRachel Younger speaks to Orit
OL,7,FZadikevitch, a close friend of the
OL,8,FBerman family who describes herself as
OL,9,Fa second mother to twins Gali and Ziv
OL,11,FFor Orit Zadiktevitch, the last two
OL,12,Fyears have been hell. On October 7,
OL,13,Fher children's father and their uncle
OL,14,Fwere brutally murdered by Hamas
OL,15,Fmilitants. Two of her son's best
OL,16,Ffriends, Gali and Ziv Berman, who were
OL,17,Fso close to the family they considered
OL,18,FOrit their second mother, were taken
OL,19,Fhostage.
