OL,3,C'Second mum' to hostage twins on the
OL,4,Cdesperate wait for their release
OL,6,FThen there was just an agonising
OL,7,Fsilence.
OL,9,FThe only proof of life came 18 months
OL,10,Finto their captivity, when another
OL,11,Freturning hostage said he had seen
OL,12,Fthem, but many months before his
OL,13,Frelease. It left family and friends
OL,14,Fwith no idea if Gali and Ziv were
OL,15,Falive or dead, until Wednesday night
OL,16,Fwhen their names suddenly appeared on
OL,17,Fthe list, handed over by Hamas, of 20
OL,18,Fliving hostages.
