OL,3,C'Second mum' to hostage twins on the
OL,4,Cdesperate wait for their release
OL,6,FNow Orit and other members of Kibbutz
OL,7,FKfar Aza are preparing to welcome the
OL,8,F28-year-olds home.
OL,10,F"I can't sleep now for good reasons,"
OL,11,Fshe told me. "Before that, I couldn't
OL,12,Fsleep for bad reasons. We are all the
OL,13,Fmothers together. We are all the
OL,14,Ffamilies together."
OL,16,FShe said families and friends would
OL,17,Fgather together to celebrate the
OL,18,Fhostages' release as a community, as
OL,19,Fthey had mourned as one.
