OL,3,C'Second mum' to hostage twins on the
OL,4,Cdesperate wait for their release
OL,6,F"We want to be together. It's a
OL,7,Fcommunity. We suffer together. And now
OL,8,Fwe want to be together to be happy,
OL,9,Ffinally again," she said.
OL,11,F"We cannot stop thinking about the
OL,12,Fpeople that we lost. But we want, for
OL,13,Fa few hours, to be happy, not to act
OL,14,Fhappy, but to be happy from the
OL,15,Finside."
OL,17,FThis strongest of women, who hasn't
OL,18,Fmissed a Saturday protest in support
OL,19,Fof the hostages for two years, wept as
OL,20,Fshe told ITV News. "Gali and Ziv are
OL,21,Falive. They're coming back."
