OL,3,C'Second mum' to hostage twins on the
OL,4,Cdesperate wait for their release
OL,6,F"I didn't give birth to them, but
OL,7,Fthey're my kids. This is why I used to
OL,8,Fsay to everyone these things. There
OL,9,Fare my kids. And imagine... your kids
OL,10,Fare gone. And you don't know if
OL,11,Fthey're alive. Think about your kid.
OL,12,FIf for two hours you don't know where
OL,13,Fhe is. You start to make phone calls."
OL,15,FShe added: "We have to see them alive.
OL,16,FThis is the first step. And then we
OL,17,Fcontinue."
