OL,4,Cdesperate wait for their release
OL,6,FSixty-four members of Orit's community
OL,7,Fwere killed on October 7 after Hamas'
OL,8,Frampage through the kibbutz, including
OL,9,Fher former husband, who she described
OL,10,Fas the love of her life, and her
OL,11,Fbrother-in-law. Orit went to eight
OL,12,Ffunerals a day for two weeks in the
OL,13,Faftermath of the attack.
OL,15,FHamas-led militants stormed into
OL,16,FIsrael on October 7, 2023, killing
OL,17,F1,200 people and taking 251 hostage.
