OL,3,C'Second mum' to hostage twins on the
OL,4,Cdesperate wait for their release
OL,6,FIn Israel's ensuing offensive, more
OL,7,Fthan 67,000 Palestinians have been
OL,8,Fkilled in Gaza and nearly 170,000
OL,9,Finjured, according to Gaza's Health
OL,10,FMinistry.
OL,12,FIsrael is set to release around 2,000
OL,13,FPalestinian prisoners in exchange for
OL,14,Fthe remaining hostages.
OL,16,FSeveral weeks ago, Orit's son got
OL,17,Fengaged to his long-term girlfriend.
OL,18,FWhen he told her, his mother replied:
OL,19,F"Don't do it without Gali and Ziv."
