OL,6,FThey know, after more than two years
OL,7,Fin captivity, that the twins'
OL,8,Frehabilitation will take time. But
OL,9,Fthey will be patient before setting a
OL,10,Fwedding date.
OL,12,F"And then," smiled Orit. "We are going
OL,13,Fto have such a celebration. And
OL,14,Fthey'll be there"
